snippet.title: brainchildpl
snippet.description: On this channel I will be creating 3d low poly game art in Blender 3d. I've been creating 3d and 2d art for games for last 12-14 years. I created GUI and Game Interface Design for games, Game Icons, Lowpoly Game Assets, High Poly models, Sculpts in Zbrush, Photoshop and Blender. I also use Substance Painter and Substance designer in my workflow - I love procedural texturing and I love working with node system. I use Unity for my games but I want to also learn Unreal Engines to create 3d art for that game engine - so stay tuned, I will have more game asset creation workflows for Unreal and Unity Game Engines.
